{"tid":859251,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"無時無刻都記住mc jin對lin","createTime":"2018-10-12T11:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T14:04:45.000Z","uid":74876,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f771cfd5aa3a6c23cccf4b66099207dae8e66af","tid":859251,"uid":74876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T11:19:50.000Z","msg":"17歲那日不要臉<br />\n春卷既挑戰<br />\n明星係無訓練班<br />\n乒乓1夾已登天<br />\n<br />\n喜歡我 別遮臉🤤🤤🤤<br />\n黎明顏射塊臉<br />\n他早洩 全因睇過部戲秋生哥渲染<br />\n來唱咸歌 齊齊來1遍<br />\n無時無刻都記住mc jin對lin<br />\n朝偉淫魔 同劉華作挑戰<br />\n但成龍有錢 爭鬥難避免<br />\n阿嬌膽怯 栢芝糾結<br />\n萬幾張是佢張臉<br />\n<br />\n騰原拓海的賓州唔亮劍！！"},{"pid":"9c408e7ea8b3d83d20edbc1ad486029b702b72bd","tid":859251,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T11:24:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6382d72538a978463a3e0ae3611cb8d329f23ce","tid":859251,"uid":19560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c408e7ea8b3d83d20edbc1ad486029b702b72bd","tid":859251,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T11:24:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T14:02:33.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩"},{"pid":"c7aed6f646c884e51ca4ab7722fbc71a326cb942","tid":859251,"uid":171107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b6382d72538a978463a3e0ae3611cb8d329f23ce","tid":859251,"uid":19560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c408e7ea8b3d83d20edbc1ad486029b702b72bd","tid":859251,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T11:24:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T14:02:33.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T14:04:45.000Z","msg":"戇撚柒鳩"}]}